{
  "stem": "2230.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it wasn't-- you-- you expected to live so long as you pushed that push cart and you dug those stones out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But you were not killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] From there I was taken to-- one day they came in with a-- loaded all of us up and put us into train.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it must have been 10 years, I guess, we were in that train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know how long it was, going back and forth and back and forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we each had a spoon that you got your soup with to eat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we left, we took the tools with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So some of us knocked on the spoon at the edge with a stone until it became sharp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every day or so, they would stop and open the trains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had a bucket over there to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Same bucket was used for water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] So a few of us decided to cut it out, to escape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How do you escape?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't know where you are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You don't know what you're doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we figured it can't be worse than it is now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's got to be the end, so might as well do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we started to cut the boards from that train with that spoon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The spoon became sharp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a knife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we cut out a board.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one night, we started to jump out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of us in the-- in the train, in the cattle car, a lot of us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know by name who they were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were lots of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was packed.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
